# administrativeArea

**Instance Property**

The name of the state or province of the place.

## Declaration

```swift
administrativeArea?: string;
```

## Discussion

For example, the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/Place/administrativeArea] for Golden Gate Park in San Francisco, California, is “`California"`.
